snippet.textDisplay: Tesla has really shown all the car guys of the world that it’s only a matter of time before everything has gone full electric simply because it’s the best option for performance. Performance cars always stem from the highest level of motor sport and before long F1 and other types of high level racing will have no choice but to go full electric for the sake of having the fastest cars out there. Once that happens every other performance car will begin scrapping their internal combustion engines as well. What I’m getting at here is that Tesla has shown consumers and car people that even their lower level cars will absolutely spank even the best performance cars out there in a drag race and in 0-60 times which is all people really care about anyways. It really puts into perspective how primitive combustion engines are and how much better the electric cars can be once the technology becomes more affordable for everyone to own. Not only that but imagine owning a Tesla, a car that you never have to take to the gas station, you just plug it in at home. 90% of your cars use is likely for commuting which means you don’t even need to really care about the battery life of your Tesla and it also means you never need to worry about all the traditional bullshit that comes along with owning a combustion engine car. The Tesla’s are just far better, period. It’s only a matter of time before car shows like this will be pitting an electric supra and an electric mustang up against each other.

snippet.textDisplay: A Porsche 911 is what it is, a superb "afordable" sports car, better quality than the tesla but less practical, more expensive , more sophisticated handling in any way and with a lovely engine sound !!! The 911 is impressive but more impressive is the Model 3 because as an family car and being more practical than the 911 and much heavier  , it can be as fast or faster in any acceleration speed you choose and can stop at the same distance with the Porsche !!! I wish I could have them both , a fast accelerating roomy and silent car and on the other hand a fun to drive car with impressive engine sound and handling and fast too!!!
